treatments.name: Lumpectomy + Sentinel Lymph Node Biopsy
treatments.response: Complete resection achieved. 2/15 lymph nodes positive. Margins clear.

treatments.name: AC-T Chemotherapy (Doxorubicin/Cyclophosphamide followed by Paclitaxel)
treatments.response: Completed all cycles. Partial response. Manageable side effects including fatigue and neuropathy.

treatments.name: Adjuvant Radiation Therapy
treatments.response: Completed 25 fractions. Good tolerance. Local control achieved.

treatments.name: Tamoxifen 20mg daily
treatments.response: Maintained remission. Switched due to bone metastases detection.

treatments.name: Letrozole 2.5mg + Palbociclib 125mg
treatments.response: Currently on treatment. Bone metastases stable. CA 15-3 trending up slowly. Tolerating well with mild neutropenia.
